OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a cold start this morning
OL,6,Fwill be dry and bright. Clouding over
OL,7,Fthis afternoon with some patchy rain
OL,8,Fspreading from the northwest.
OL,9,FFreshening northwesterly winds in the
OL,10,Fnorth later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain will spread south across
OL,13,Fall parts for a time this evening.
OL,14,FThen becoming mainly dry during the
OL,15,Fearly hours with clearing skies. Cold
OL,16,Fwith some patchy frost.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FAll parts will have a dry day
OL,19,Fwith variable amounts of cloud and
OL,20,Fsome sunny intervals. Rather cold.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
